    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">Figures inspirantes</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/be%CC%81ne%CC%81diction%20apostolique.jpg?itok=vrh3Dp-V" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content"></div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/les-100-ans-du-p%C3%A8re-beaubien">Les 100 ans du Père Beaubien</a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p><a class="documents" href="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/documents/CENTENAIRE%20%20IRE%CC%81NE%CC%81E%20BEAUBIEN%20%20%20CORRECTION.pptx" title="Évocation des 100 ans du P. Beaubien">Évocation des 100 ans du P. Beaubien</a><br /><strong>Le téléchargement peut prendre 2-3- minutes ... mais ça vaut la peine !</strong><br />
	Diaporama préparé par Madame Christiane Richer à la Résidence Notre-Dame-de-Richelieu.</p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even">
    
      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">Réfugiés</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/JRS_Canada_2.jpg?itok=QETVd-0y" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content"></div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/arriv%C3%A9e-du-25000e-r%C3%A9fugi%C3%A9-syrien-au-canada">Arrivée du 25.000e réfugié syrien au Canada</a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p>Le gouvernement canadien a tenu sa promesse. Bravo! Et bravo à toutes les personnes qui ont contribué à cet effort collectif. Bien que cela paraisse peu dans un contexte où 4 millions de Syriens se sont réfugiés en Turquie, au Liban et en Jordanie, c’est 25 000 personnes de moins qui vivront la peur et la misère.</p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd">
    
      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">Prier au quotidien</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/Capture_1.JPG?itok=NyVa1biC" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content"></div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/4-au-12-mars-%E2%80%94-neuvaine-de-la-gr%C3%A2ce">4 au 12 mars — Neuvaine de la grâce</a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p>La neuvaine de la grâce a lieu du 4 au 12 mars, durant les jours qui précèdent l’anniversaire de la canonisation de François Xavier, le 12 mars 1622.<br /><a href="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/documents/NEUVAINE_2016.pdf">Voir le dépliant de la neuvaine</a></p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-4 views-row-even">
    
      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">Haïti</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/LogoRegard.JPG?itok=7pOIjSCt" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content">Bulletin d&#039;information du territoire d&#039;Haïti</div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/le-regard">Le Regard</a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p>Consulter ici le bulletin d'information du territoire haïtien de la Compagnie de Jésus.</p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-5 views-row-odd">
    
      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">Haïti</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/Ha%C3%AFti.jpg?itok=csRW-bxn" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content">Crise électorale</div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/communiqu%C3%A9-de-presse-du-centre-social-j%C3%A9suite-de-port-au-prince">Communiqué de presse du centre social jésuite de Port-au-Prince</a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p>Le CERFAS exprime sa préoccupation dans la crise électorale en Haïti. Cette préoccupation devient de plus en plus inquiétante avec l’immixtion du Core Group dans le processus électoral.</p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-6 views-row-even">
    
      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">Décès</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/Ringuet%20crop.jpg?itok=WdCBI0wN" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content"></div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/p-pierre-ringuet-sj">P. Pierre Ringuet, S.J..</a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p>P. Pierre Ringuet, S.J., décédé à la communauté Jean-de-Brébeuf de l’infirmerie de Richelieu, mardi 26 janvier 2016, à l’âge de 93 ans, après 72 ans de vie religieuse.</p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-7 views-row-odd views-row-last">
    
      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-category">            <h2 class="field-content">100e anniversaire de naissance</h2>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-visual">            <span class="field-content"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.jesuites.org/sites/default/files/styles/image_front_preview_/public/Beaubien.JPG?itok=ioSi_FbG" width="210" height="167" /></span>    </span>      
    <span class="views-field views-field-field-toptitle surtitre">            <div class="field-content"></div>    </span>      
    <h3 class="views-field views-field-title">            <span class="field-content"><a href="/content/le-p-ir%C3%A9n%C3%A9e-beaubien-sj">Le P. Irénée Beaubien SJ </a></span>    </h3>      
    <div class="views-field views-field-body">            <div class="field-content"><p>Ce mardi 26 janvier 2016, c’était jour de fête à la communauté Jean-de-Brébeuf de Richelieu. On y a célébré, dans la joie et l’action de grâce, le 100e anniversaire du P. Irénée Beaubien, pionnier de l'oecuménisme au Canada.</p>
</div>    </div>   
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
